{"tid":1578591,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"(重點整理）「靜坐日」與「感謝日」之階段報告","createTime":"2019-09-18T07:49:07.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-18T13:44:00.000Z","uid":21545,"like":46,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":30,"replies":[{"pid":"1dc70a709adc52e77288ce86e1592d76cf13e2dd","tid":1578591,"uid":21545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T07:49:07.000Z","msg":"（忽發奇想）如果今個禮拜遊行又被反對 不如整一個「靜坐日」同「感謝日」<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1574316\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1574316</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n靜坐日 （922）（與商場靜坐同一日）<br />\n<br />\n目前我嘅睇法係 以一枱叫一杯可樂為symbol (為畫面夠juicy) 塞爆扑野家與MX 如果多人就輪姦佢  <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n活動為和理非 勿破壞 勿嘈交 勿騷擾其他市民 建議可自備紙牌 到時舉起 作無聲抗議 <br />\n <br />\n地點首選：沙田分店<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 配合靜坐日 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n感謝日 （921）<br />\n由於日間有河妖搞事 所以建議大家盡量避免接觸佢地 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我地可以用呢一日嘅日間去支持黃絲食店 食完之後打卡上傳 幫佢地宣傳下<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  以實際行動表達謝意<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n晚間先去重建Lennon wall 或到元朗靜坐 <img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/kiss.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n簡單易做 所有人均可參加 尤其適合有心有金冇力之手足 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n目前需要：<br />\n文宣圖 作宣傳 <img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n黃絲餐廳list <img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9e0fe17c3371960f6299c14b71174d30f8213ef0","tid":1578591,"uid":117906,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T07:49:25.000Z","msg":"<stron